Rake is a [[Ruby]] "[[Make]]" build utility.

### Example Rakefile
This is about as simple as it gets (this file is named "Rakefile"):

<pre class="sh_ruby">
task :default do
    puts "hi"
end
</pre>

when I run "rake", it puts "hi".

